{"tid":198594,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"賊爆石油氣行 煮食器具同gas都偷埋","createTime":"2017-04-12T15:25:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-12T15:25:23.000Z","uid":73262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"06a5bed98c4f1eb5a1e373ba06085b5199a990e5","tid":198594,"uid":73262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T15:25:23.000Z","msg":"今晨9時許，深水埗北河街一間石油氣行，職員返回開舖時，發現店內有搜掠痕迹，抽屜被撬，懷疑遭賊匪潛入爆竊，於是致電報警。警員到場經初步調查，發現店舖的後門被撬，相信賊匪由該處潛入犯案。經點算後，證實損失近6,000元，包括300元現金，3箱gas及5個煮食器具。<br />\n<br />\n根據資料，過去4個月，深水埗區已先後發生多宗涉及石油氣行的爆竊案，當中長發街的石油氣行損失逾6萬元財物，包括一批紅酒及兩部手提電腦等。<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56553491&amp;category_guid=10829391&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170412\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56553491%26category_guid%3D10829391%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170412&d=7FLALsszV4LuAMmN05fc6sn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=aa8c2926\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56553491%26category_guid%3D10829391%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170412&h=e8e4f610\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56553491&amp;category_guid=10829391&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170412</a>"}]}